  <summary>5/23/1988--Passed House amended.
(Measure passed House, amended) Amends the Agricultural Act of 1949 to: (1) extend the prohibition on an extra long staple cotton cross compliance requirement through the 1990 crop year; and (2) prohibit any increase in a producer's total crop acreage base as a result of such cross compliance exemption.</summary>
